_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":184301,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3468,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":495944,"username":"shawnliu03","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shawnliu03","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ef7939c894c3410b168a56d67fcf7ee2?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ef7939c894c3410b168a56d67fcf7ee2?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ef7939c894c3410b168a56d67fcf7ee2?s=73&d=retro","created":1592864389,"last_modified":1592864389},"last_reply_by":"icyalala","last_touched":1651640860,"title":"业余玩家如果进行 iOS 开发","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/850721","created":1651622628,"deleted":0,"content":"背景：iPad 上有一款笔记软件 Note Always 我很喜欢，可惜开发者很久没有更新，自己有些需求想满足可没有其他软件能替代。于是萌生自己开发的想法。\r\n主要需求是自己开发自己用，做得还行就开源出去。自己以前也没开发过 iOS app 算是给自己培养个爱好。\r\n自己情况：算法选手，啥都用 Python 。C++有点大学里写数据结构的底子。\r\n打开 Xcode 新建项目看着有点晕，借宝地咨询一下如何正确开始 iOS 开发，不求多么高级的架构只要自己能玩玩就行。","content_rendered":"<p>背景：iPad 上有一款笔记软件 Note Always 我很喜欢，可惜开发者很久没有更新，自己有些需求想满足可没有其他软件能替代。于是萌生自己开发的想法。\n主要需求是自己开发自己用，做得还行就开源出去。自己以前也没开发过 iOS app 算是给自己培养个爱好。\n自己情况：算法选手，啥都用 Python 。C++有点大学里写数据结构的底子。\n打开 Xcode 新建项目看着有点晕，借宝地咨询一下如何正确开始 iOS 开发，不求多么高级的架构只要自己能玩玩就行。</p>\n","last_modified":1651622628,"replies":9,"id":850721},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_large.png?m=1650095232","name":"go","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_normal.png?m=1650095232","title":"Go 编程语言","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/go","topics":2254,"footer":"","header":"Go 是一个开源的编程语言，它能让构造简单、可靠且高效的软件变得容易。","title_alternative":"The Go Programming Language","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_mini.png?m=1650095232","stars":3138,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":375,"parent_node_name":"programming"},"member":{"id":350715,"username":"godlovesxcjtest","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/godlovesxcjtest","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d116/cea4/350715_mini.png?m=1578316020","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d116/cea4/350715_normal.png?m=1578316020","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d116/cea4/350715_large.png?m=1578316020","created":1537352441,"last_modified":1578316020},"last_reply_by":"godlovesxcjtest","last_touched":1651638277,"title":"Go 的 html/template 把我的模板自动给转码了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/850741","created":1651632677,"deleted":0,"content":"模板代码如下：\r\n```go\r\n{{- define \"common/web/atom\"}}\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\r\n    <feed xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\">\r\n\r\n    </feed>\r\n{{end}}\r\n```\r\n\r\n很简单的一个代码，主要是想用来实现一个 atom 服务器，返回浏览器 atom.xml 文件\r\n\r\n\r\n但是调用 ExecuteTemplate 方法后，变成了这个样子:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n```xml\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\r\n    <feed xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\">\r\n     \r\n    </feed>\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n尖括号\"<\" 变成了 &lt; \r\n\r\n很奇怪的一个问题。我知道 Go 的 html/template 会对一些输入进行转码，避免把用户的输入生成到 html 。\r\n\r\n但是为什么会把我的模板里面的也进行转码了呢","content_rendered":"<p>模板代码如下：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-go\">{{- define \"common/web/atom\"}}\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?&gt;\n    &lt;feed xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\"&gt;\n\n    &lt;/feed&gt;\n{{end}}\n</code></pre>\n<p>很简单的一个代码，主要是想用来实现一个 atom 服务器，返回浏览器 atom.xml 文件</p>\n<p>但是调用 ExecuteTemplate 方法后，变成了这个样子:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">\n\n&amp;lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?&gt;\n    &lt;feed xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\"&gt;\n     \n    &lt;/feed&gt;\n\n</code></pre>\n<p>尖括号\"&lt;\" 变成了 &lt; </p>\n<p>很奇怪的一个问题。我知道 Go 的 html/template 会对一些输入进行转码，避免把用户的输入生成到 html 。</p>\n<p>但是为什么会把我的模板里面的也进行转码了呢</p>\n","last_modified":1651632677,"replies":8,"id":850741},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":10707,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":5544,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":296314,"username":"cathiabi","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cathiabi","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2fb0042e3511baca6bad8837c7dab8ac?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2fb0042e3511baca6bad8837c7dab8ac?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2fb0042e3511baca6bad8837c7dab8ac?s=73&d=retro","created":1520091910,"last_modified":1520091910},"last_reply_by":"cpstar","last_touched":1651635309,"title":"北京联通， iptv 卡顿","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/850725","created":1651627562,"deleted":0,"content":"iptv 使用 udpxy 转单播，隔一段时间后会有不定时的卡顿，重启光猫后正常。\r\n\r\n不知道有没有人遇到类似问题？或者可以在不重置的前提下拿到 /登录光猫超管的？型号为 ZXHN F477V9 。","content_rendered":"<p>iptv 使用 udpxy 转单播，隔一段时间后会有不定时的卡顿，重启光猫后正常。</p>\n<p>不知道有没有人遇到类似问题？或者可以在不重置的前提下拿到 /登录光猫超管的？型号为 ZXHN F477V9 。</p>\n","last_modified":1651627562,"replies":8,"id":850725},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ede7/e2b6/867_large.png?m=1651565527","name":"vscode","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ede7/e2b6/867_normal.png?m=1651565527","title":"Visual Studio Code","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/vscode","topics":509,"footer":"","